draw((B + C)/2--Ap);
draw((A + C)/2--Bp);
draw((A + B)/2--Cp);

label("$A$", A, A);
label("$B$", B, B);
label("$C$", C, C);
label("$A'$", Ap, Ap);
label("$B'$", Bp, Bp);
label("$C'$", Cp, Cp);
[/asy]

solution:
Note that the perpendicular bisectors meet at $O,$ the circumcenter of triangle $ABC.$

[asy]
